ource": "arXiv CS ML", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.20295v1/2603.20295v1/figs/online_intro.png", "score": 10}, {"id": "oai:arXiv.org:2603.20209v1", "title": "Children's Intelligence Tests Pose Challenges for MLLMs? KidGym: A 2D Grid-Based Reasoning Benchmark for MLLMs", "summary": "Abstract: Multimodal Large Language Models (MLLMs) combine the linguistic strengths of LLMs with the ability to process multimodal data, enbaling them to address a broader range of visual tasks. Because MLLMs aim at more general, human-like competence than language-only models, we take inspiration f...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.20209", "source": "arXiv NLP", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.20209v1/2603.20209v1/x1.png", "score": 10}]}